        "evidence": "<p>The GI-GPA is calculated by the addition of the selected points:</p>\n<table border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 246.382px; border-width: 1px; border-style: none;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 33.27645051194539%;\"><col style=\"width: 33.27645051194539%;\"><col style=\"width: 33.27645051194539%;\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\"><strong>Variable</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\"><strong>Points</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"height: 67.1952px; border-width: 1px;\"><calculator id=\"3168\">Karnofsky Performance Score</calculator></td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">&lt;80</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">80</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">90-100</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"height: 44.7968px; border-width: 1px;\">Age, years</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">&ge;60</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">&lt;60</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">0.5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"height: 44.7968px; border-width: 1px;\">Extracranial metastases</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">Present</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">Absent</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">0.5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"height: 67.1952px; border-width: 1px;\">Number of brain metastases</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">&gt;3</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">2-3</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">0.5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
        "facts": "<p>Interpretation:</p>\n<table border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 246.382px; border-width: 1px; border-style: none;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 49.91596638655462%;\"><col style=\"width: 49.91596638655462%;\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\"><strong>GI-GPA Score</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\"><strong>Median Survival (months)</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">0-1</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">1.5-2</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">9</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">2.5-3</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">12</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">3.5-4</td>\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; border-width: 1px;\">17</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
