        "logic": "//Declare vars\nvar kps = parseFloat(kps);\nvar age = parseFloat(age);\nvar em = parseFloat(em);\nvar num = parseFloat(num);\n\nvar score = kps + age + em + num;\nvar survival;\n\nif (score <= 1) {\n    survival = 3\n} else if (score <= 2) {\n    survival = 9\n} else if (score <= 3) {\n    survival = 12\n} else {\n    survival = 17\n};\n\nvar calc_output = [];\n\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'mini',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: 'GI-GPA Score'\n})\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'score',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: 'GI-GPA Score'\n})\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'survival',\n    value: survival,\n    value_text: 'months',\n    message: 'Median Survival'\n})",
